  <brief_title>Optimized Chemotherapy Followed by Maintenance With Bevacizumab With or Without Erlotinib in Treating Patients With Metastatic Colorectal Cancer That Cannot be Removed by Surgery (DREAM)</brief_title>
  <acronym>DREAM</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase III Study of an Optimized Chemotherapy Followed by Maintenance With Bevacizumab Strategy With or Without Erlotinib in Unresectable Metastatic Colorectal Cancer. DREAM OPTIMOX 3. C04-2</official_title>
  <sponsors>
